summary: Small improvements to the LOD tree textures
descriptionHtml:
This small mod contains a slightly changed the original texture for the LOD trees.

I never liked how flat the trees in the background look, so I tried to make it a little better.
At least with my settings it works ;)
Biggest improvement is visible on the trees around the Riften area.
Check the screenshots for comparison.

Just unpack the file into your Skyrim\data directory.

If you don't like it, just delete the file.
